Walter Brooke https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Walter_Brooke 0 Walter Brooke (born Gustav William Tweer Jr.; October 23, 1914 – August 20, 1986) was an American actor. Brooke is best known for playing Mr. McGuire in the 1967 hit film The Graduate, where his character famously said "Plastics".
